title: Baba Vanga’s Chilling 2026 Alien Warning Coming True? Trump’s UFO Move Shocks World
description: Baba Vanga’s chilling 2026 alien prophecy is back in the spotlight after President Trump ordered the release of UFO and UAP-related government files. The Bulgarian mystic once predicted that a “massive spacecraft” would enter Earth’s atmosphere in November 2026 — proof we are not alone. Now, with Washington reopening the alien debate following comments by former President Obama, speculation is surging online. Is this coincidence, political theater, or the beginning of a historic disclosure? Watch

title: What Barack Obama said about UFO files that made Donald Trump say "he made a big mistake"
description: President Trump has ordered the release of government files concerning UFOs and extraterrestrial life, citing immense public interest. This follows former President Obama's remarks on the topic. While the US government acknowledges Unidentified Aerial Phenomena (UAP) are real, reports indicate no confirmed extraterrestrial origins, with many sightings attributed to mundane objects or advanced US technology.
